<h3>Visitors &amp; General Viewers Any information held about visitors is purely statistical.</h3>

This information will include, but will not be limited to, the browser you use, the operating system you use, your ISP designated IP address [not your personal computers's IP], which web page you were redirected from, and date and time of your visit and which pages have been viewed.

If you have any queries regarding privacy and data protection please contact the administrator: <a href="administrator@thephantoms.co.uk">mailto:administrator@thephantoms.co.uk</a>

<h3>Databases &amp; Data Protection</h3> 
No personaly identifiable information will be held on our records unless authorised by the individual. If in any case there is a questionable piece of content that appears to breach UK data protection, please make the editor aware by emailing the administrator: <a href="administrator@thephantoms.co.uk">mailto:administrator@thephantoms.co.uk</a> so that the offending content can be investigated and if necessary, be removed forthwith.
